title: Danielle Bradbery - The Heart Of Dixie [MP3@320 -Complete Tags i
description:
image
Danielle Bradbery just might be the breakout superstar that 'The Voice' desperately needs.

Channeling such influences as The Dixie Chicks and Carrie Underwood, Danielle's debut single "The Heart of Dixie" is a sweet, uplifting tale of a woman caught between a dead-end job and a dismisive alcoholic husband. She finally comes to her senses and leaves it all behind her.
